commit.message:
Fix UMA fetch (brotli/stream), expand to 50 entries, add UMA Date column

- http.py: remove br from Accept-Encoding (requests can't decode brotli);
  switch get_html to stream+iter_content to tolerate IncompleteRead
- uma_idx.py: add _parse_uma_pdf_paths() for IDX Nuxt SSR format
  (extracts YYYYMMDD-WAS_UMA_XXXX.pdf patterns, filters to last 90 days);
  add Indonesian-language fallback URL; retry 403 like 429
- config.yml + config.py: UMA max_count 20 → 50
- routes/anomaly.py: _fetch_uma_cached returns dict[ticker→date];
  screen result includes uma_date field
- templates: add UMA Date column; replace IDX link with detail page link;
  Intl.NumberFormat id-ID formatting; sortable numeric columns
- utils/parse.py + tests: parse_number() strips thousand separators

Co-Authored-By: Claude Sonnet 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>
